// THIS SECTION IS AUTO-GENERATED - DO NOT EDIT MANUALLY
//
// Go tooling generates go.sum content when you:
//   - Run 'go build' (downloads dependencies)
//   - Run 'go mod tidy' (cleans up dependencies)
//   - Run 'go get [package]' (adds new dependencies)
//   - Run 'go mod download' (pre-downloads dependencies)
//
// What Gets Added:
//   - Checksums for every downloaded module version
//   - Checksums for go.mod files of each dependency
//   - Checksums for transitive dependencies
//
// What Gets Removed:
//   - 'go mod tidy' removes checksums for unused dependencies
//   - Checksums stay even if dependency is indirect
//
// Why Multiple Versions:
//   - Build tried version A, then upgraded to version B
//   - Different build constraints selected different versions
//   - go.sum keeps history for reproducibility
//
